title: Snowflake Web UI Tour — All Tabs Explained in Simple Words
description: A simple, story-driven guide to exploring the Snowflake Web UI. Learn about all tabs, panels, and menus, and understand how to navigate, manage warehouses, databases, and queries like a pro.
